This folder contains all the accounts that have registered with the server.
when a username logs in it checks the corresponding ./accounts/{} folder for
files associated with an account.

/accounts/
/accounts/admin/             (super-user)
/accounts/admin/pass.salt    (salted password file)
/accounts/admin/characters/

refresh salt on username login.


/accounts/andrew/            (regular-user)
/accounts/andrew/pass.salt
/accounts/andrew/characters/
